  "title": "SB 1072 - This act exempts the state of Missouri from the advancement of time provision known as Daylight Saving Time in federal law.  The state of Missouri and its political subdivisions shall observe the standard time of the United States as provided in federal law.\r\n\r\n\tThe provisions of this act become effective on November 1, 2026.\r\nJIM ERTLE",
